  },
  "CardHelpSection": {
    "ParentObjectID": "advanced_copper_tools_tea_blending_station_lit",
    "LocalizationKey": "Advanced_Copper_Tools_TeaBlendingStation_Lit_CardHelpSection",
    "DefaultText": "<b>Slots (×6):</b> Herbs dry faster while lit. Use 'Grind All' to mill dried or millable items. <b>Water Tank:</b> Drag any container with water to add a Water Charge (max 8). Drag an empty clay bowl to draw boiled water — requires at least 1 Water Charge AND Water Temp ≥ 50%. Consumes fuel over time."
  },
